title: 2022–23 Asian Tour
text:
The 2022–23 Asian Tour will be the 27th season of the modern <a href="Asian%20Tour">Asian Tour</a>, the main men's <a href="professional%20golf%20tour">professional golf tour</a> in Asia excluding Japan, since it was established in 1995.
